{"tid":518732,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"世紀大騙案 牛奶是沒有鈣的(?)","createTime":"2018-01-03T15:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T11:51:02.000Z","uid":151789,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"206583d05759c76c00c09635b7354542f05b5474","tid":518732,"uid":151789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:42:38.000Z","msg":"話說小弟今日係OK屎忽痕，睇各牛奶營養成份，發現除左有列明&rdquo;高鈣&rdquo;嘅，部份牛奶成份係冇鈣嘅<br />\n細細個老師就教我，牛奶係高鈣飲品，咁哩啲牛奶到底有冇鈣？求指教<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/234133_4a83eb442082f4d0a6ed8e0225a891fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F234133_4a83eb442082f4d0a6ed8e0225a891fb.jpg&h=851cac4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/234138_e3fbd547de910bf03ad3278682756885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F234138_e3fbd547de910bf03ad3278682756885.jpg&h=c50f84f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/234141_696371b0e510c8754f074886fdac6deb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F234141_696371b0e510c8754f074886fdac6deb.jpg&h=6e2203d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/234143_c1f52b4d56270944ee78e9b91378c13f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F234143_c1f52b4d56270944ee78e9b91378c13f.jpg&h=1d1f18d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9d813714058c1e66588697795ca6a19cfcb6380","tid":518732,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"206583d05759c76c00c09635b7354542f05b5474","tid":518732,"uid":151789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:42:38.000Z","msg":"話說小弟今日係OK屎忽痕，睇各牛奶營養成份，發現除左有列明&rdquo;高鈣&rdquo;嘅，部份牛奶成份係冇鈣嘅<br />\n細細個老師就教我，牛奶係高鈣飲品，咁哩啲牛奶到底有冇鈣？求指教<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/234133_4a83eb442082f4d0a6ed8e0225a891fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F234133_4a83eb442082f4d0a6ed8e0225a891fb.jpg&h=851cac4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/234138_e3fbd547de910bf03ad3278682756885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F234138_e3fbd547de910bf03ad3278682756885.jpg&h=c50f84f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/234141_696371b0e510c8754f074886fdac6deb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F234141_696371b0e510c8754f074886fdac6deb.jpg&h=6e2203d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/234143_c1f52b4d56270944ee78e9b91378c13f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F234143_c1f52b4d56270944ee78e9b91378c13f.jpg&h=1d1f18d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:47:37.000Z","msg":"真係無留意到原來有啲牛奶係無鈣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50c97f5dd4937d66d0f78603e3a135d04ff05f8","tid":518732,"uid":86400,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"冇寫唔代表冇<br />\n香港營養標籤唔一定要寫鈣落去"},{"pid":"2d2267b76c784e4cec1eada46d340055162983d5","tid":518732,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0855e98e0839fe9b6eae260dd78e81bfd9afde","tid":518732,"uid":123456,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:55:50.000Z","msg":"佢冇話有水tim啦"},{"pid":"dd6a4c92c7c39bd7c7104aaa937d840e9e05d7c4","tid":518732,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"舊時有寫出黎<br />\n記得係高鈣奶一半左右<br />\n可能考慮marketing 唔寫<br />\n<br />\n你睇吓其他牌子有冇？"},{"pid":"6a55b8a7154eb2a260c7a1ebe58437850434beac","tid":518732,"uid":120236,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"唔係咩新鮮事, 牛奶不嬲對補鈣都冇乜幫助架啦, 300cc牛奶先得果300mg鈣, 但人一日要補1200mg鈣, 所以我有食鈣片"},{"pid":"be05a6500749a96fe6c392a08151041d0518c763","tid":518732,"uid":120733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:31:09.000Z","msg":"我都食緊jamieson隻鈣, 佢有埋維D可以幫助吸收, 單單鈣都有機會吸收唔到"},{"pid":"7755160385bdca2d78b429a4ca790f478954a786","tid":518732,"uid":29880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:31:58.000Z","msg":"ON9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b86edbd3de58558fa0de0b7bc6665af8fa7a58","tid":518732,"uid":160926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"有冇鈣其實睇營養標籤係唔清楚嫁 <br />\n因為工作需要會處理到有關營養標籤問題 所以我略知一二<br />\n每個地方要求嘅營養標籤有所不同<br />\n香港嘅營養標籤必須列明嘅係7+1<br />\n1: <br />\n能量(Energy)<br />\n7: <br />\n蛋白質(Protein)<br />\n碳水化合物(Carbohydrates)<br />\n總脂肪(Total Fat)<br />\n飽和脂肪酸(Saturated fatty acids)<br />\n反式脂肪酸(Trans fatty acids)<br />\n鈉(Sodium)<br />\n糖(Sugars)<br />\n<br />\n而其他例如維他命 鈣 鉀之類不必列明喺標籤<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>除非</strong></span>個包裝標明左係高鈣等字眼，就必須喺營養標籤列明<br />\n<br />\n希望可以解惑<br />\n<br />\n但以我所知牛奶都係有calcium"}]}